          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "LU-11726 osd: export mballoc stats",
        "message": "LU-11726 osd: export mballoc stats\n\nlctl set_param osd-ldiskfs.?.mb_stats=1 to enable and reset\nlctl set_param osd-ldiskfs.?.mb_stats=0 to disable\nlctl get_param osd-ldiskfs.?.mb_stats to dump.\n\nIO load distribution can be found in:\n/proc/fs/osd-ldiskfs/*/io_distribution\nwith 3 columns: #index reads writes\n\nIO seeks (calculated in 16K units can be found in:\n/proc/fs/osd-ldiskfs/*/io_seek\nwith 3 numbers: sum seeks, number of seeks, avg.seek\n\nChange-Id: Ic65e027287b4bb1a1fd73ebc6e89e92577c86953\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_10"
    }
  },
